Class Vector

  • java.lang.Object
    • asteroids.Vector
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    Direction, Position, Velocity

    public class Vector
extends java.lang.Object
    A superclass for vectorial properties, such as position, velocity, acceleration, direction... Implemented for the sake of economy.
    Version:
    0.0
    Author:
    Syd & Xavier
